香港衰左好開心既垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:51:38.000Z","msg":"邊個搞衰香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你訓醒未"},{"pid":"b7de29eb4b401396d8f83705157418b96d7774e3","tid":633504,"uid":46128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:56:41.000Z","msg":"一齊有咁折墮得咁折墮就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但啲有錢佬都係大把後路逃生門，只會窮人含撚</span>"},{"pid":"6f2681c50161f0a09d41b28d529e401dcb9aa60e","tid":633504,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:57:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>雨革魚革見到咁激烈抗爭個陣仲有少少希望<br />\n後來好快就做左真焦土派<br />\n我諗唔少人同我一樣已經對個d乜乜超支僭建貪污dq唔比人選無哂感覺 只覺得 哦係咩 係咁架啦 或者當下笑話睇<br />\n唔跌過唔知死 反正都係政府自己造成</blockquote><br />\n你地咪搞衰香港，到時候呢講呢嗰個港女比啲大陸仔un,你地西都冇得屌，成班以為香港衰左好開心既垃圾</blockquote>邊個搞衰香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你訓醒未</blockquote><br />\n你話點就點，你覺得唔關心放棄係好就得，反正死果個係你，我仲有選擇權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4322093728e1591a54d3c91bec417c2c21eefb9c","tid":633504,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:21:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab39dec8434ce5c58a9b009d02e68943a63295f3","tid":633504,"uid":128032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"點可以咁快就麻木同放棄架..."},{"pid":"daf2405256ff032da68192037ae659b41a42ab2f","tid":633504,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b61c28564b7dbe4adc49cf689fec6e8da8e21834","tid":633504,"uid":20058,"like":102,"dislike":1,"score":101,"quote":{"pid":"3c69ec8cfa75d2bf451da1653fd500fef6ba0b8b","tid":633504,"uid":53687,"like":69,"dislike":2,"score":67,"quote":{"pid":"51645574c0e13eee35da029444315aeda6ce5c5d","tid":633504,"uid":3742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:18:41.000Z","msg":"雨革魚革見到咁激烈抗爭個陣仲有少少希望<br />\n後來好快就做左真焦土派<br />\n我諗唔少人同我一樣已經對